]. Which will still take a while."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "692.631","u": "[In Russian] And what are you studying now?"},    {"who": "Boleslaw Czolopicki", "start": "695.700","u": "[In Polish] At the moment I&#39;m learning the radio."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "698.522","u": "[In Russian] The radio. Are you paying to study at this school?"},    {"who": "Boleslaw Czolopicki", "start": "706.798","u": "[In Polish] Up to now, I&#39;m paying at that school."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "710.276","u": "[In Russian] You&#39;re paying?"},    {"who": "Boleslaw Czolopicki", "start": "711.825","u": "[In Polish] But here, I&#39;m to be paid for. In this school . . ."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "719.340","u": "[In Russian] And your school, is it a day school? Do you have some job in Paris?"},    {"who": "Boleslaw Czolopicki", "start": "724.433","u": "[In Polish] No. I mean, so far, I worked, but now, because I signed up for that course, I&#39;ve stopped working. And here that course will be paid for."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "737.326","u": "[In Russian] Aha, and where in Paris do you live?"},    {"who": "Boleslaw Czolopicki", "start": "743.341","u": "[In Polish] At Le Bonoir [?]"},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "746.733","u": "[In Russian] Do you pay for your lodgings, or is it communal living for many Poles?"},    {"who": "Boleslaw Czolopicki", "start": "755.133","u": "[In Polish] No, I live in a hotel."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "758.287","u": "[In Russian] Have you any relatives in America? Any members of your family in the U.S.?"},    {"who": "Boleslaw Czolopicki", "start": "768.370","u": "[In Polish] No. I have no relatives in America."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "770.900","u": "[In Russian] You have no relatives in America. And what do you plan to do: will you stay in France, or something else?"},    {"who": "Boleslaw Czolopicki", "start": "777.936","u": "[In Polish] I would most like to emi