                                                                                                <b>Boleslaw Czolopicki</b>
                    <p class="utterance">[In Polish] The moment that on the 5th of October 1944 the Germans deported . . . the entire population of Warsaw . . . er . . . to Germany. It&#39;s a bit hard for me . . .</p>
